{"title":"常青树","authors":["肖韶光"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":7,"day":8}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"常青树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肖韶光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在井冈山大井毛泽东旧居墙后，并排长着两棵树，红军下山后，被白匪用火烧死，直到全国解放，两棵树同时奇迹般地爆出新绿，且至今郁郁苍苍，故被称作“常青树”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一立足就起点很高"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这里并肩联手"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"头顶漫天阴晴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脚底根基如磐"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"纳日精月华为底蕴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"矢志不渝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为大地常青而常青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"据说树的历史"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与两个人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连同一个国家的命运有关"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生命的浓荫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵护偌大的红色摇篮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"猎猎树冠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为当日昏睡的民族"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昭示出生机无限"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那年朱毛远征去"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"腥风血雨浓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草木过火石过刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长夜熬天明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"忽报枝头闹春早"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈人使出喊山劲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“哎呀嘞———"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"朱毛进京去赶考哟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金榜题了名”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚贞守护这方圣土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山一般沉默"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看彻几多过眼烟云"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将人间沧桑融入每条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"叶脉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为共和国的常青"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高高扬起祝福的手臂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哦生命奇观"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"世纪遗产"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国特色的不朽风景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞻仰者说"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"常青两棵树"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"犹如井冈人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"井冈人说不"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵像毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一棵像朱德"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}